{"tid":1262422,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港反送中變咗國際向中共施壓嘅把柄，習大大今舖多得林鄭唔少","createTime":"2019-06-27T16:30:53.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-27T16:58:55.000Z","uid":159913,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"e1ff88beab584e181d030ed80ec99a951611f733","tid":1262422,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:30:53.000Z","msg":"因為以林鄭為首嘅港共政府龜縮，遲遲唔肯拆彈<br />\n今次G20凡係唔gur中共嘅國家元首見到習總都可以撚吓佢香港嘅事<br />\n<br />\n咁要面嘅習總返嚟會點對付林鄭? <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: pink;\">雖然香港人都可能受報復</span>"},{"pid":"0f8ea13551e356deef8ad6be563cfbbadbac12bd","tid":1262422,"uid":159913,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:37:54.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://mgmresearch.com/wp-content/uploads/2019/01/G20-Countries-Flags.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fmgmresearch.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2019%2F01%2FG20-Countries-Flags.png&h=582c99ea&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n已講: 日本<br />\n=============<br />\n較大可能會講: 美國、加拿大、英國、德國、法國、澳洲、歐盟<br />\n<br />\n不太可能會講: 意大利、墨西哥、韓國、印度、巴西、南非、阿根廷<br />\n<br />\n肯定唔會講: 俄羅斯、土耳其、印尼、沙特阿拉伯<br />\n<br />\n有冇人開盤<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c48ba46b540a7eeecc9bf85a1aafc3ff2117d7bb","tid":1262422,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:39:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d5c11ffff65b834f7c865193ab6207e360d3b642","tid":1262422,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:41:13.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"7617d278c26ff63436f34aaf03a36fd26ddadae9","tid":1262422,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:41:55.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"edf0d1219599fdee457e6f9948c1c32f1342286f","tid":1262422,"uid":159913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-27T16:42:52.000Z","msg":"